There are **two condition** robot will go in Circle loop.
1. instructions endpoint at (0,0)
2. instructions not equal to **N**(direction) and endpoint not equal to (0,0)

**explanation**:

![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/32a83430-2a50-4175-ad6b-59212e022485_1600393925.7353935.png)

